<br>
Also, as a mild-carpal tunnel syndrome ranger, I can assure that using archery for extended periods of time is definitely NOT something you can do while afk.<br>
<br>
As far as rebalancing, I don't see the need for any huge changes.  Warriors do need taunt fixed, and monks could use a little tweek to get their dps up some.  I think most of the other melee classes are fine though.  As a ranger, I think we're fine- don't tinker with us!  The only thing I'd like to see is an auto-attack for range attacks but that's probably not going to happen.<br>
<br>
